_gid=ApiCkH5M4gqU6z_ez9aHrCY&oh=00_AYAqoT4IPbPAgzUIBVXF7xFEdKmYPC4PYNVQ-_BdotnL7A&oe=66EC1651"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Rock & Rails", "keywords": ["Rock", "Rails", "Shooter", "Music", "Cooperative"], "long_description": "The world of Rock \u2018n\u2019 Roll has been silenced, so it\u2019s time to get loud! Take up guitars and basses, and blow up the Silence Beasts with a BAAANG! Ride on rails all over the city, shredding riffs solo or jamming with your friends, and reclaim our world back in the name of Rock!\n\n- 9 levels full of rock and metal\n- 3 eligible characters\n- Metal Mode - harder levels for hard rockers\n- Local Co-Op Mode - jam with a friend*\n\n* Requires two devices with the game installed and a WiFi connection to play in co-op mode.", "short_description": "The world of Rock \u2018n\u2019 Roll has been silenced, so it\u2019s time to get loud! Take up guitars and basses, and blow up the Silence Beasts with a BAAANG! Fly over the place shredding riffs solo or jamming with your friends, and reclaim our world back in the name of Rock!"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "248799673186091", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Rock & Rails", "keywords": ["Rock", "Rieles", "Disparos", "Musica", "Multijugador"], "long_description": "El mundo del rock fue silenciado. \u00a1Es hora de subir el volumen y cambiarlo! Toma tu guitarra y bajo, y destruye a las Bestias del Silencio con un sonoro estruendo. Desliza por rieles que llevan a todo tipo de lugar, ya sea solo o tocando con amigos, \u00a1y reclama nuestro mundo de vuelta en el nombre del Rock!\n\n- 9 niveles llenos de rock y metal\n- 3 personajes elegibles\n- Modo Metal - niveles m\u00e1s dificiles para rockeros hardcore\n- Modo Cooperativo Local - juega con un amigo*\n\n* Requiere dos tel\u00e9fonos con el juego instalado y una conexi\u00f3n WiFi para jugar en modo cooperativo.", "sho